      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## The Frightening Part\n+\n+- Edge routing/ELK feels risky because it touches HU master branch of visualization and state.\n+- Mistakes can break renderers or reintroduce animation kit (`GSAP`) conflicts.\n+- The orientation goal is to understand the scope and lock down contracts/telemetry before implementation."
      }
