      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Orientation Guidelines\n+\n+- Build a dedicated layout panel (ELK controls) inside the presentation layer so the editor owns the knobs.\n+- Emit layout intents via `useIntentEmitter` so the interpreter/validator pipeline already listens.\n+- Keep contracts flexible, versioned, and summarized (no extra restrictions) while the panel surfaces the important options."
      }
